---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import QuickSummary from '../components/QuickSummary.astro';
---

<Layout title="Base Building" description="Building and research priorities from new player to mid-game in Last War: Survival.">
  <h1>Base Building</h1>

  <QuickSummary>
    <p><strong>Early game:</strong> Rush HQ level. <strong>Mid-game:</strong> Only upgrade buildings and research that directly power your main squad.</p>
  </QuickSummary>

  <h2>Building Priority Order</h2>
  <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm">
    <li><strong>HQ</strong> — Unlocks everything else. Push this hard early rather than spreading resources across other buildings.</li>
    <li><strong>Troop Center</strong> for your main squad type (Tank/Aircraft/Missile).</li>
    <li><strong>Research Lab</strong> — Focus on combat, troop load, and training speed for your chosen type.</li>
    <li><strong>Gear Workshop / Enhancement buildings</strong> — Critical once you start getting good gear.</li>
    <li><strong>Resource buildings</strong> — Only what you actually need to support training and healing.</li>
    <li>Everything else (Barracks, Hospital, etc.) can wait or be upgraded minimally.</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Research Priorities (New → Mid Game)</h2>
  <div class="table-wrapper">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Phase</th><th>Focus Areas</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Early</strong></td>
          <td>HQ tech, basic troop training, resource production, first combat upgrades.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Mid-Game</strong></td>
          <td>Troop load, march size, type-specific combat research, skill-related tech, gear enhancement speed.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Do Not Rush</strong></td>
          <td>Most economy buildings past the point you can support your main squad, decorative buildings, late-game prestige tech.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[#8a96b0]">The biggest trap is upgrading every building to the same level. Many buildings give almost no meaningful power until very high levels. Stay focused on what helps your #1 squad today.</p>
</Layout>